\id 1PE - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG 1 Peter 01 22/3/91 Macnaughtan
\h 1 PIDA
\toc1 Pidamaęž‰ tapaeyeke titinaęž‰ wapee
\toc2 1 Pida
\toc3 1 Pida
\mt1 Pidamaęž‰ tapaeyeke titinaęž‰ wapee
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 IĚ± Pida Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ Aposolomaęž‰ iki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ maĚ±leke lia mea halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mo aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰laęž‰leke da yoka tankulupu mea pua iki ta Pondasi kenke o Kaęž‰leisia kenke o Kaęž‰padosia kenke o Eisia kenke kutupa make mo Bidinia do kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pankaęž‰ halo peleme wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ do wape pitolome.
\v 2 Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ tekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ iki maĚ±leke lia miaęž‰me. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ dupa Mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ iki yakopiki wandaęž‰hali hamenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ make Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ pi opua puemenaęž‰ make kutupa ipikaęž‰ wemaęž‰ iki tandepenaęž‰ make iki mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki make iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tumbaenaęž‰e.
\p 
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi lomanaęž‰e. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ mieke handa Yesu Ketiso homa paa tiaeyeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ panake daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kiaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰ hone ti laasaęž‰eki tumbao halaęž‰me.
\v 4 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke ale manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ minaęž‰ mombaęž‰la wialaęž‰ ekie. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ do ale manutaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mulumeke hone ti lao halomaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo otaęž‰ epeke ale manutaęž‰ hepeni nane kukutu na pu o na hoyo make honipa puaęž‰peke na yo piaęž‰peke ale paęž‰taęž‰ wialaęž‰me. Mo ale manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki wiawalaęž‰me.
\v 5 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo paetolo natenaęž‰ peneme yao opolo epenaęž‰ anaęž‰lao halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yu wia haaso hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasemeke handa ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki handeteke halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 6 Ametaęž‰ tekipuleke laaseme haumanu make handolo hataęž‰ hosikimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homo halemepate mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wiawalaęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 7 Mo tekipuleke laasaęž‰ haumanu ipulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki yaaluekemaęž‰ ipu halaęž‰me. Kenke paęž‰taęž‰ awa minaęž‰laęž‰ kolotaęž‰ hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate kone haliwekimaęž‰ otaęž‰ kolope o hoke ekipe laa pa handuluekemaęž‰ timaęž‰ yanka hando halememe. Koto piteleme tupaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekinaęž‰ takaęž‰lao hamenaęž‰ la handilieke. Mo kolotaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke ale yaęž‰laęž‰pate kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kolo make otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me. Takaęž‰lao haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ opolo ipilie natenaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki mu paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki mu titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la haasaęž‰eki mu pilimikie.
\v 8-9 Ipikitaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ na handemepate kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelememe. Ametaęž‰ ipiki lekemaęž‰ na handelemepate kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halememe. Ikaęž‰ temokonaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone tulaememe. Kutupa ametaęž‰ minelemeke handa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao lombei pu pa pua otaęž‰ pimaęž‰ make lapeke na yeke taęž‰naęž‰ homo halememe.
\p 
\v 10 Mo paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone uluekemaęž‰ ambaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halao hayeke potopede haliwekimaęž‰ ekipape alo hataęž‰ weiyu haemekeme. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pa hameke kulu pieke ekinaęž‰ mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ laęž‰ wimikime.
\v 11 Ketisonaęž‰ temokomaęž‰ mo potopede haliweki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ Ketiso ipikaęž‰ tanda mulu piekeeki make ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ telimea epolo piekeeki make laęž‰ wia waleeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hau manutaęž‰ ekipa handimaęž‰ ipiliepe laa handuluekemaęž‰ weiyu taapo haemekeme.
\v 12 Do hande opimi otaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ walaaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Mo wetepenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰eki peneme yao waleekeme. Mo Pi Seliaponaęž‰ kinki peaasaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ hepeni nanemaęž‰ tapaeyeke Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ do otaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kimime. Do otaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo enisolo haliwekimaęž‰ kone hone uluekemaęž‰ hone pu halememe.
\p 
\v 13 Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ peaęž‰peke hau hone hone u hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa leke leke lo hapaęž‰peke. Yesu Ketiso opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki kilieke. Kotoeki homekenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone ti lao hao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 14 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua pu hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa iki mateyaęž‰ di ninaęž‰ hone tiaemeeki manumaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ikaęž‰ halemeeki na handeteke haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke.
\v 15 Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ iki wi leaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yako piki hali halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki make ikaęž‰ hau paeyao tonkaęž‰naęž‰ yako pea hapaęž‰peke.
\v 16 Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yako piki hali halo ekinaęž‰ iki make yako piki wandaęž‰hali hapaęž‰peketaa laęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ yenki tiekemaęž‰ niki hambaęž‰ miekeeki
\p 
\v 17 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni pitolo hataęž‰ Apaęž‰o lo haleme Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao homeke hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ iki homeke homekemaęž‰ pu haeme haunaęž‰ pi yokaęž‰ alu pilieke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ame do kenkenaęž‰ haleme natenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 18 Ikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ kieke mimi napeke na pitu epe na piki hau manunaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ yenki haleeke ekitaęž‰ iki hone wilimime. Mo yenkitaęž‰ manimanu silipa o kolo hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ mani ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 19 Ketisonaęž‰ we otaęž‰ seliapomaęž‰ iki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ hoyo alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki (Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia halo haemeke) sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ ikiki leke hayekeme.
\v 20 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke aĚ±iĚ± na wepieke pitaęž‰maęž‰ kone Yesu ambaęž‰ mea hayekeme kutupa do wetepe nanetaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ ipiki peneme yaeyekeme.
\v 21 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulalememe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu mea tiao paĚ±aĚ± peawayekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulalemeeki make ikaęž‰ hone ti lalemeeki make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pu halememe.
\s1 Nikaęž‰ Ketiso tapake paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hamanaęž‰e
\p 
\v 22 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pi opua pu haleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ temoko yako pinaęž‰ lelememe. Ame ikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke otaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homa halememe. Koto pelemepate ikaęž‰ puki paeyaomaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ otaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 23 Ikitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki hamenaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki hamenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ pimaęž‰ iki paa mendiaeyekeme.
\v 24 Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ pa opaęž‰laęž‰ ambu tupaęž‰ halememe. Kutupa ikaęž‰ au lo halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambunaęž‰ moma opaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo ambu hapitolotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ moma make alupilieke.
\q1 
\v 25 Kutu piliepate mo Tekehalinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ na paeke pa u halieke.
\p Koto pitaęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰ Pi Seliapoe.
\c 2
\s1 Tekehali ipikitaęž‰ daęž‰ta ulaęž‰ toopi seliapo ulaęž‰me
\p 
\v 1 Hoke hau paeyao baapaęž‰peke. Yayapiki pi na lo makeaasaęž‰ hau na pu maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ epeke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰peke yeke honditi pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau na pu kutupa make kake neli pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi na lapaęž‰peke.
\v 2 Panake mendiaęž‰laęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ andu naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ temoko tambaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ yako piki andu naęž‰naęž‰ lo hapaęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo andu no haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ daeya hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki milimikie.
\v 3 Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ epeke hau pu halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ naa handememe.
\p 
\v 4 Tekehalitaęž‰ mo daęž‰ta ulaęž‰ toopi paęž‰taęž‰ ipu hapaęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ koto toopitaęž‰ pa alee hone wia kiao haemekeme. Koto pimikipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo toopitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epekeekie la maĚ±leke liekeme.
\v 5 Iki make daęž‰ta halaęž‰ toopi ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ halememe. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mea ipikaęž‰ yakopiki temokonaęž‰ da aęž‰enaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Do da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yako piki yeni peao halaęž‰ haliweki hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ minaęž‰ ikaęž‰ temoko Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 6 Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke toopi homeke maĚ±leke lia ametaęž‰ Saioni nane da kini piaęž‰peke toopi winaęž‰ ulume. Kutupa koto toopi paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halie hali epitaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homilieke.
\p 
\v 7 Iki hone tulaleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me hone u halemepate mo hone na tulaleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 Da aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ kiaemeke toopitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ tumiki toopi kone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Baibolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰
\q1 Do toopimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali halaęž‰mbaęž‰ liaenaęž‰ lelieke laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa koto toopi tiekemaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰hali lopenaęž‰ lelieke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\m Iki halaęž‰mbaęž‰ liaemeke ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pinaęž‰ hone na tulaemeke ekinaęž‰ piekeme. Kototaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone piekeekie.
\s1 Nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tapake halomaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 9 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ tapake halememe. Ikitaęž‰ mo Kini halinaęž‰ yeni peao haleme wandaęž‰halie. Ikitaęž‰ mo yakopiki tapakee. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homeke halememe. Ikitaęž‰ mo timbaęž‰laęž‰ pambeke paęž‰taęž‰ haapaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ epoemenaęž‰ wi leaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu la halamenaęž‰ iki maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me.
\v 10 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ iki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali na haemepate ametaęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki halememe. Ambaęž‰taęž‰ iki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau hone na wimipate ametaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau aęž‰paęž‰leke melememe.
\s1 Nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali halomaęž‰me
\p 
\v 11 Ya yankeke tonuo. Iki do kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰eileke epeleme na handeke wandaęž‰hali leke hamenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ honke alo ekitaęž‰ dupa Ikaęž‰ temoko aęž‰ndaęž‰ lu tiaasaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ waleke na wiao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 12 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi na maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali taapunaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau pu hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikinaęž‰taęž‰ hande pi na maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki biki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ taapilimipate ikaęž‰ epeke piteleme ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie. Koto ekinaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hande laęž‰ ulaęž‰ nate epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki aęž‰meiyalimikie.
\p 
\v 13 Ikaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ Kapomaninaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao opua homu pea hataęž‰ mo Kini you hali hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ make
\v 14 kutupa ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make homu pea hapaęž‰peke. Mo you halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ mo hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali panisi haluekemaęž‰ make mo epeke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki aęž‰meiyaluekemaęž‰ make tapaeyekeme.
\v 15 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa Mo hone na wiki wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ napeke na wiki pi aleme ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke hau piteleme ekimaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ puemenaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me.
\v 16 Kaęž‰laęž‰pa halaęž‰ haliweki leke hapaęž‰peke. Iki kaęž‰laęž‰pa haleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke haumanu aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaseme wandaęž‰hali hapaęž‰peke.
\v 17 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone u ikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo kutupa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homo kutupa mo Kini you hali paęž‰taęž‰ make epeke hone u hapaęž‰peke.
\s1 Yesu teliolo hataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki mulumeke
\p 
\v 18 Eki epimaęž‰ yenki e pokawaaseme wandaęž‰hali haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ e teke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Hone wotu wia aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰ teke hali tonu paęž‰taęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo aĚ±iĚ± mineke panko halaęž‰ teke hali tonu paęž‰taęž‰ make kutu piaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 19 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekinaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa hameke iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki hone witolo hataęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mea tia haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mea epeaalieke.
\v 20 Otaęž‰ hoke hau pimi ekinaęž‰ panisi peaaso haenaęž‰ minolo halimipate kone kotaęž‰ haunaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki ekipa mea aęž‰meiyaliepe. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau pu halimipate koto haunaęž‰ kone maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ minolo hamenaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mea epeaalieke.
\v 21 Koto piki hau puemenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki wi leekeme. Kotaęž‰ Ketiso ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ miekeme. Kutupa mo handa piekeeki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ telia puemenaęž‰ yeke walolo piekeme.
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyao na piekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ kake hambilikimaęž‰ yayapiki pi na leekeme. Wandaęž‰hali paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na opimikime.
\v 23 Kutupa haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi alo ipikaęž‰ loke mandaęž‰ meaemeketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke pi la hombo na peayekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mieke dinaęž‰taęž‰ dupiki hoke yenki milimikie la hombo na peayekepate Kodaęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao halaęž‰ pi yokaęž‰ alu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lao hayekeme.
\v 24 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ homomono kutupa tikitiki hau paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hamono Ketisomaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau mea tia aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape ti manda peekeme. Ipikaęž‰ loke lieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki daęž‰taalaęž‰me.
\v 25 Ambaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ alu pimi sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ leke haemepate ametaęž‰ mo sipisipi handeteke halaęž‰ hali tomuemenaęž‰ hatuku mea epeleme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ temoko handeteke halaęž‰ halie.
\c 3
\s1 Tooli toolinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 1 Koto tupaęž‰ kone weteke tonu ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ haliki tonu paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hao hapaęž‰peke. Mandane haliki tonumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi na miki haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke hau pilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliweki pi minaęž‰ yolaęž‰ milimikie.
\v 2 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ pi na miki haliki tonu paęž‰taęž‰ pi homeke kone na lo haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ homu pea epeke yakopiki hau seliapo pilimieki handataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ kutu pilimikie.
\v 3 Loke yole epeke hake wandaęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ manda lokenaęž‰ au anipu lapaęž‰peke. Do hau manunaęž‰ alome. Ikaęž‰ itiki ponkaęž‰ pilu o belekemanu wotu moko kutupa mo akaęž‰ epeke epeke yamo halemeeki manunaęž‰ alome.
\v 4 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikaęž‰ loke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ otaęž‰ wandaęž‰ do koto wandaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ yole epeke haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Koto yole pea haasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoto paeyao epeke tupaęž‰ hao hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo kimele piki hau make homu piki hau make koto hau yole yaapotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handataęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau tieke hone u halaęž‰me.
\v 5 Mo ambaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lao haemeke yako piki wandaęž‰ wekitaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki yole pinaęž‰ lemekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ haliki tonu oto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.
\v 6 Setataęž‰ kutu piki wandaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ pi opua hataęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ya teke halio laęž‰tiki piekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke epeke hau pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ waneke tonu halememe.
\p 
\v 7 Haliki tonu iki make haliki hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ iki tupaęž‰ honkopu na halememe hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰weki iki make iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa hameke kitaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ milimikie. Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni pu haleme ekimanu saęž‰saęž‰ na pinaęž‰ koto hau pu hapaęž‰peke.
\s1 Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pea hamanaęž‰e
\p 
\v 8 Ya paeyaaso pitaęž‰ dupa alome. Iki paeyaomaęž‰ hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone wia aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke. Iki homeke homeke paeyaomaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ yankeke homeke hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pea make epeke hau pu alualu pea make homu pu alualu pea hapaęž‰peke.
\v 9 Hoke hau iki paęž‰taęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoke haumaęž‰ na hombo peapaęž‰peke o keke pi lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ keke pimaęž‰ na hombo peapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hau na pikitaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mulu peleme ekimaęž‰ hombo peapaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki wi leaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mulueke la laęž‰ wiekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Kotaęž‰ Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰
\q1 Epimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make epeke tupaęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki make handuluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lo halaęž‰ hoke hoke pi make yayapiki pi make minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 11 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau hoki wala epeke hau pinaęž‰e. Kutupa make aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰ hau handa puluekemaęž‰ tolu weiyu haenaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 12 Pa ekipeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali handeteke hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni pu halemeeki hoto paeyao opu halaęž‰me. Kutu pu halaęž‰pate mo hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoki wala aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia hao halaęž‰me.
\s1 Epeke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 13 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hau puluekemaęž‰ honemaęž‰ wotu homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epimaęž‰ iki hoeyaaliepe.
\v 14 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate epeke hau pitolo hataęž‰ kone kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wotu homaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke hone baapaęž‰peke.
\v 15 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Tekehali haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone ti lao haleme ekitaęž‰ ekipape la lotaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo pealuekemaęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 16 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone witolo hataęž‰ homu pikimaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ hone teke tikitiki yao halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone haenaęž‰ lo hapaęž‰peke. Koto pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki mo Ketisonaęž‰ hoki nane teliaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ epeke hau pu halemeeki handataęž‰ mo mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do hautaęž‰ hokeekie lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ koto leme ekinaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ yeke ikaęž‰ hone teke tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke.
\v 17 Nikaęž‰ epeke hau pulumaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mulumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pate nikaęž‰ hoke hau pulumaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mulumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kototaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Ketisomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau yoko luekemaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homeekeeki
\p 
\v 18 Ketiso hone umanaęž‰e. Ipiki kone ikinaęž‰ homeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau paeyao yoko luekemaęž‰ hoto homeke kone homeekeme. Niki Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku poluekemaęž‰ mo epeke halimaęž‰ niki hoke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ anke teke mea homeekeme. Ipikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lemekepate ipikaęž‰ temokotaęž‰ (Kodaęž‰maęž‰) daęž‰ta hao haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa temoko hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo dipula pitimiki temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ pua (Kodaęž‰naęž‰) pi waleekeme.
\v 20 Mo temoko manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande Noamaęž‰ mo kawaso eiyeke pitaęž‰maęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ temokomanue. Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi minaęž‰ yu wia handeteke hayeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi na opimikime. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo hande kawaso tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hombo aęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paeyaotaęž‰ ketepo hataęž‰ mo ikalimaęž‰ peteleekeme.
\v 21 Koto ikalitaęž‰ mo hande wetepenaęž‰ bapitaisi hau epolo piekeeki manda mieke ikalie. Do ame pu haleme bapitaisi haumaęž‰taęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± tandaęž‰ pelemeeki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate ikaęž‰ epeke hone tekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hamenaęž‰ mo ikalimaęž‰ iki petolo halaęž‰me. Do bapitaisi hautaęž‰ mo Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ paa tiaeyeke ekimaęž‰ iki petolo halaęž‰me.
\v 22 Koto Ketisotaęž‰ ame hepeni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua Kodaęž‰naęž‰ popeke nane hataęž‰ mo enisolo haliweki make hepeni nane haleme you haliweki make mo wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make iki paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰me.
\c 4
\s1 Ambaęž‰ halaęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰lao topo pumanaęž‰
\p 
\v 1 Ketiso ipikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ tanda mieke handa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tanda mulu piekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wieke tupaęž‰ koto mandake honemaęž‰ kone iki honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ tanda mu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau minaęž‰paęž‰lao halaęž‰me.
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ ame do anetaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tiaaseme ekimaęž‰ iki na handeteke haenaęž‰ leketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki handeteke haenaęž‰ lo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 3 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau pu haleme hau pimime. Koto haunaęž‰taęž‰ nate anaęž‰naęž‰ paeyaememe. Mo yolaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make leke polaęž‰paasaęž‰eki make hoke ikali naa keaasaęž‰eki make (ne hoke ikali tieke pamba naa keao) siakaęž‰ hake hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make mo yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yo mokaęž‰laapeke na yo piki yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make koto hau manunaęž‰ ikaęž‰ nate paeyaememe.
\v 4 Kutupa mo pi na opiki pa haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ame do ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ mo hande siakaęž‰ haumanu apaęž‰tao na pu haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ penkilipaataęž‰ iki hoke tupaęž‰ laalememe.
\v 5 Kutu pu halemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali make ambaęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali make pi yokaęž‰ alu puluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu tiki epeme (hoke) haumanu otaęž‰ la halimikie.
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Pi Seliapo waleekeme. Wandaęž‰hali paeyao ikaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki mu haleme tupaęž‰ iki make ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki mimikime. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ temoko make daęž‰ta hao haenaęž‰yeke mo hande Pi Seliapo iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleekeme.
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ e pokomanaęž‰e
\p 
\v 7 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ paeyolo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ nunaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni (anaęž‰naęž‰) puluekemaęž‰ leke leke lo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone wopu wia hapaęž‰peke.
\v 8 Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau eleke eleke aęž‰mbao haleke handa ikaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 9 Tulu tulu na leke ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu ane pitulu endi mone pitulu endi pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 10 Iki homeke homekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ta kaęž‰laęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki manutaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kieke taęž‰taęž‰ piki ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hameke epeaaluekemaęž‰ pu alualu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 11 Epimaęž‰taęž‰ pi walo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi homeke walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰taa. Epimaęž‰taęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ wele taapunaęž‰ hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰taa. Koto ekinaęž‰ do hau paeyao pilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lapeke yelieke. Mo paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make mo kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki make ipikaęž‰eki na paeke pa hao halieke. Kutu pinaęž‰e.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ tapake hataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 12 Ya yankeke tonuo. Mo iki la handaęž‰laęž‰ ti talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeke tanda minelemeeki handataęž‰ dotaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lataęž‰ na penkili peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 13 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ putu piliki minolomaęž‰me laa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki opolo ipilie pitaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ tumbalieke.
\v 14 Ikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ teliaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haleme ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± piki temokotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ temoko kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ pitiaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me.
\v 15 Mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ ku halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali litaęž‰laęž‰ hali haleme ekinaęž‰ o pake nalaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haleme ekinaęž‰ o pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haleme ekinaęž‰ o mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hau hoeyake pi alo dupi dupi pi lo halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haleme ekinaęž‰ kutu piki haumanu pu haleme ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰
\v 16 koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo Ketisonaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali halemeke handa kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰ minelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeketaęž‰ iki Ketisonaęž‰ biki miniki haleme ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi lo hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ ame ambaęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali kone paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la kini pu mea pi yokaalu pilieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la kini piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo opua kone pa kiaaseme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ekipa paeyaaliaęž‰pe
\v 18 Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Epeke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali peteluekemaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ hone na wiki hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki hau pealiaęž‰pe.
\m 
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone paęž‰leke handaa kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haleme epeke hau manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaleme ekitaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ Wepia Ulaęž‰ Hali ipikaęž‰ pi na yambolo halaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 5
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke halaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 1 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ you hali weki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± make you hali hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yaasaęž‰ pi alome IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ tanda miekeeki handoaęž‰ halie. Kutupa mo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make mulueke.
\v 2 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke hamenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Kimaęž‰ na homeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Do e pokaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ yenki homekenaęž‰ hone na wiki ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone hone pitolo haenaęž‰ pokaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 3 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke hamenaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tumbaaluekemaęž‰ na tapeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pu halimi epeke hau manumaęž‰ mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu wala tiaaso hataęž‰ hapaęž‰peke.
\v 4 Kutupa mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ Titinaęž‰ Hali opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± na alu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ namba otaęž‰ seliapo pikieki kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ milimikie.
\s1 Hone tikitiki yao homu pea hapaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 5 Koto mandake tupaęž‰ kone iki panake panake haliwekimaęž‰ make mo keileke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hao hapaęž‰peke. Kutu paęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ homu pea ha alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ akaęž‰ leke yama hao hapaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hakoko litaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kiao halaęž‰pate mo homu pea halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki halo halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele wopu piki kiki oto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ homu pea hao hapaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone piliaęž‰ di ninaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki mea aęž‰meiyalieke.
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ witeleme hone eleke eleke paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lopa moneaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 8 Leke leke lo hataęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipulaęž‰eki handoemenaęž‰ potaęž‰ pua tunkulu hapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki hali Sadanimaęž‰ mo sayale hali maęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ handa wandaęž‰hali lia noluekemaęž‰ wei mea pomu halaęž‰me.
\v 9 Mo kenke paeyaonaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Ketiso tapake wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mandake tupaęž‰ tanda minelemeeki make hone wia hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu tulao hataęž‰ Sadani pendulu baapaęž‰peke.
\v 10 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali hataęž‰ iki Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hamenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ nate paeyao paĚ±aĚ± pu halaęž‰eki muemenaęž‰yeke iki ambaęž‰ wi laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ tanda peaasaęž‰eki hosiki hao paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone wetepe iki epeaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu hao daĚ±oĚ±la hamenaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 11 Mo Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ weletaęž‰ hoto paeyao Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pu haenaęž‰e. Aowe otaęž‰e.
\s1 Ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taloe pi
\p 
\v 12 Do dokaęž‰tiki tameiyaęž‰taęž‰ Silipanisi ya kame teke paęž‰taęž‰ ekimaęž‰ wape peaenaęž‰ wape pea puaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki saęž‰saęž‰ pealuekemaęž‰yeke ya otaęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ mo laęž‰tiki epolo pi paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ekie alome. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ do aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ daĚ±oĚ±la hao hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 13 Do Baęž‰biloni kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme siosi tapaketaęž‰ iki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me. Koto siosi tapakemaęž‰ make ya weki Makamaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe pi tapaalaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 14 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso hataęž‰taęž‰ mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kiki minaęž‰ alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu hapaęž‰peke. Iki paeyao Ketisonaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki muemenaęž‰e. 
